1
00:00:48,500 --> 00:00:52,620
=Endless Love=

2
00:00:52,700 --> 00:00:55,540
=Episode 19=

3
00:01:06,879 --> 00:01:07,480
Ling Xiao,

4
00:01:07,760 --> 00:01:08,599
what brings you here?

5
00:01:12,359 --> 00:01:13,680
I didn't know where to find you,

6
00:01:14,200 --> 00:01:15,480
but we agreed to meet here,

7
00:01:16,200 --> 00:01:17,000
so I knew

8
00:01:17,879 --> 00:01:18,719
you would come.

9
00:01:19,040 --> 00:01:19,920
To be honest,

10
00:01:20,519 --> 00:01:21,599
on Qixi,

11
00:01:21,599 --> 00:01:23,040
I thought you wouldn't show up.

12
00:01:23,599 --> 00:01:25,920
I never expected you
to make yourself sick

13
00:01:26,079 --> 00:01:27,159
just to see me.

14
00:01:28,359 --> 00:01:30,920
We seem to know so much
about each other,

15
00:01:31,920 --> 00:01:34,400
yet in truth, nothing at all.

16
00:01:36,239 --> 00:01:38,400
At least you know where to see me.

17
00:01:39,040 --> 00:01:40,400
But when I want to see you,

18
00:01:40,840 --> 00:01:42,439
I have nowhere to go.

19
00:01:44,920 --> 00:01:47,120
Though we know little of each other now,

20
00:01:47,840 --> 00:01:49,560
there's always this strange familiarity
I can't shake.

21
00:01:52,000 --> 00:01:53,120
Can we start anew

22
00:01:54,599 --> 00:01:56,200
and get to know each other now?

23
00:01:56,560 --> 00:01:57,519
If you want to see me,

24
00:01:58,480 --> 00:02:00,159
go to the place we always eat at.

25
00:02:01,359 --> 00:02:01,920
Alright.

26
00:02:02,599 --> 00:02:03,319
Deal.

27
00:02:05,719 --> 00:02:07,920
How I wish we could just be here,

28
00:02:08,560 --> 00:02:09,719
free of action

29
00:02:10,159 --> 00:02:11,199
and thought,

30
00:02:12,479 --> 00:02:14,120
just gazing at the night sky.

31
00:02:18,599 --> 00:02:19,479
It's my fault.

32
00:02:19,840 --> 00:02:20,400
Rushi.

33
00:02:21,120 --> 00:02:22,840
I've lost all my memories from before.

34
00:02:23,680 --> 00:02:24,919
For who I am now,

35
00:02:25,800 --> 00:02:27,199
everything is a fresh start.

36
00:02:27,919 --> 00:02:29,919
Whether it was Mu Ruyi or Jing Liuli,

37
00:02:31,120 --> 00:02:32,280
they all feel like the distant past,

38
00:02:32,599 --> 00:02:33,680
a vague dream to me.

39
00:02:34,400 --> 00:02:35,560
I can't recall a single thing.

40
00:02:36,520 --> 00:02:38,800
We share a similar fate.

41
00:02:39,800 --> 00:02:41,000
To me, the past

42
00:02:41,879 --> 00:02:43,560
is like a castle in the air.

43
00:02:44,800 --> 00:02:46,919
I don't know my own right from wrong,

44
00:02:49,479 --> 00:02:50,120
but I think

45
00:02:50,280 --> 00:02:52,479
maybe this is a gift from fate.

46
00:02:53,360 --> 00:02:54,759
After surviving death,

47
00:02:54,919 --> 00:02:56,599
rather than dwelling on the past

48
00:02:56,800 --> 00:02:58,400
or searching for who we once were,

49
00:02:59,000 --> 00:03:01,639
perhaps we should cherish the present

50
00:03:02,280 --> 00:03:03,360
and chase the future.

51
00:03:09,840 --> 00:03:11,120
Look! A shooting star!

52
00:03:11,280 --> 00:03:12,120
It's a good omen.

53
00:03:12,280 --> 00:03:13,000
Let's make a wish!

54
00:03:13,700 --> 00:03:18,940
♪Better to meet than to miss♪

55
00:03:18,940 --> 00:03:22,940
♪Even if just for a glance♪

56
00:03:24,240 --> 00:03:24,759
Rushi.

57
00:03:26,360 --> 00:03:27,159
What did you wish for?

58
00:03:27,919 --> 00:03:29,759
I wish we won't be trapped by the past,

59
00:03:30,719 --> 00:03:32,000
but keep moving forward.

60
00:03:32,700 --> 00:03:37,180
♪Better to meet than to miss♪

61
00:03:39,400 --> 00:03:42,599
I wish nothing would burden our hearts,

62
00:03:43,879 --> 00:03:44,960
and all our wishes come true

63
00:03:46,199 --> 00:03:47,039
through all that has passed,

64
00:03:47,840 --> 00:03:48,520
all that will come,

65
00:03:50,000 --> 00:03:51,120
through time and distance,

66
00:03:52,319 --> 00:03:53,599
and through every beautiful season.

67
00:04:10,639 --> 00:04:11,719
That's what you get for being stubborn.

68
00:04:11,879 --> 00:04:12,879
Something sweet may soothe you.

69
00:04:16,279 --> 00:04:17,279
Got it,

70
00:04:17,720 --> 00:04:18,759
no spicy food for you.

71
00:04:22,460 --> 00:04:22,860
(Liu Rushi's Preferences)

72
00:04:23,920 --> 00:04:25,720
Liu Rushi loves stinky tofu,

73
00:04:26,240 --> 00:04:27,199
but no cilantro.

74
00:04:28,079 --> 00:04:29,040
When eating noodles,

75
00:04:29,279 --> 00:04:30,279
she adds three spoonfuls of vinegar.

76
00:04:30,800 --> 00:04:31,759
She loves the dumpling skin

77
00:04:32,720 --> 00:04:33,800
but not the filling.

78
00:04:34,279 --> 00:04:35,079
Good heavens!

79
00:04:35,240 --> 00:04:35,959
I've never even noticed

80
00:04:36,079 --> 00:04:37,879
these details about myself!

81
00:04:38,040 --> 00:04:39,879
What you like, what you dislike,

82
00:04:40,199 --> 00:04:41,279
I'll make a note of all of it,

83
00:04:41,959 --> 00:04:42,720
so I can make you happy.

84
00:04:43,319 --> 00:04:44,040
That's so sweet.

85
00:04:44,399 --> 00:04:46,399
I'll remember your habits too.

86
00:04:46,879 --> 00:04:47,399
By the way,

87
00:04:47,920 --> 00:04:50,560
fireworks will ring in the New Year
across the city at midnight.

88
00:04:51,199 --> 00:04:52,199
Do you like fireworks?

89
00:04:53,360 --> 00:04:54,160
No, I don't.

90
00:04:54,639 --> 00:04:55,680
Though fireworks are beautiful,

91
00:04:56,360 --> 00:04:58,680
the most dazzling light
fades in a flash.

92
00:04:59,480 --> 00:05:00,800
The most beautiful moments

93
00:05:01,240 --> 00:05:02,600
never last.

94
00:05:03,120 --> 00:05:05,000
They always leave you with regret.

95
00:05:05,360 --> 00:05:07,480
Maybe its beauty lies in

96
00:05:07,800 --> 00:05:08,839
how briefly it blooms.

97
00:05:10,800 --> 00:05:11,839
Even if our love is

98
00:05:12,680 --> 00:05:13,720
as brief as fireworks,

99
00:05:14,800 --> 00:05:15,959
I will never regret it.

100
00:05:16,040 --> 00:05:16,600
Knock on wood!

101
00:05:16,759 --> 00:05:18,360
We won't be unlucky or short-lived!

102
00:05:18,680 --> 00:05:20,199
May our love be as strong as gold,

103
00:05:20,360 --> 00:05:21,199
and may we live to a hundred years.

104
00:05:24,120 --> 00:05:24,680
Agreed.

105
00:05:26,040 --> 00:05:26,560
Ke'er,

106
00:05:27,319 --> 00:05:28,639
do you like these daggers?

107
00:05:29,879 --> 00:05:30,600
And these?

108
00:05:31,040 --> 00:05:31,519
Take a look.

109
00:05:32,759 --> 00:05:33,879
More daggers?

110
00:05:34,800 --> 00:05:36,720
Do you take me
for a heartless killing machine?

111
00:05:42,720 --> 00:05:43,560
What about protective gear then?

112
00:05:43,920 --> 00:05:44,439
Look.

113
00:05:45,759 --> 00:05:47,600
Excluding this one,

114
00:05:48,000 --> 00:05:49,639
you've given me
more than 20 pairs already.

115
00:05:50,000 --> 00:05:51,639
I only have two arms and two legs!

116
00:05:52,879 --> 00:05:54,040
Then what else do you like?

117
00:05:57,519 --> 00:06:00,120
I like sugar-coated hawthorns.

118
00:06:00,639 --> 00:06:01,959
If I'm upset,

119
00:06:02,639 --> 00:06:03,680
you can buy me some.

120
00:06:04,240 --> 00:06:06,279
Alright, anything you like,

121
00:06:06,399 --> 00:06:07,240
I'll buy it for you.

122
00:06:09,959 --> 00:06:11,040
What do you like?

123
00:06:11,399 --> 00:06:13,000
If it's within my power,

124
00:06:13,360 --> 00:06:14,240
I'll get it for you too.

125
00:06:17,040 --> 00:06:18,480
Nothing.

126
00:06:20,800 --> 00:06:21,879
I just like you.

127
00:06:25,120 --> 00:06:26,480
Then give yourself to me.

128
00:06:30,000 --> 00:06:32,000
You're so cheesy. I'll kill you!

129
00:06:34,959 --> 00:06:35,920
You wouldn't really do that.

130
00:06:47,839 --> 00:06:48,319
Here.

131
00:07:00,600 --> 00:07:01,879
Tonight is New Year's Eve.

132
00:07:02,519 --> 00:07:03,639
I have something for you.

133
00:07:04,199 --> 00:07:06,839
I have a gift for you too.

134
00:07:07,839 --> 00:07:08,759
What is it?

135
00:07:17,680 --> 00:07:18,319
I never expected

136
00:07:18,879 --> 00:07:20,680
such a coincidence.

137
00:07:21,519 --> 00:07:22,800
While I was browsing the market,

138
00:07:23,120 --> 00:07:24,920
I found this wooden carving
that looks just like you,

139
00:07:25,079 --> 00:07:25,920
so I brought it back.

140
00:07:26,079 --> 00:07:27,079
Is that how

141
00:07:27,720 --> 00:07:29,399
you truly see my face?

142
00:07:29,920 --> 00:07:30,959
Because when I see it,

143
00:07:31,199 --> 00:07:33,120
I remember the way you smile.

144
00:07:34,079 --> 00:07:34,720
And you?

145
00:07:35,279 --> 00:07:37,199
Why did you give this to me?

146
00:07:38,920 --> 00:07:40,040
To make a wood carving,

147
00:07:40,759 --> 00:07:41,639
people select the wood,

148
00:07:42,560 --> 00:07:43,240
shape the rough form,

149
00:07:43,879 --> 00:07:44,519
carve the details,

150
00:07:45,240 --> 00:07:45,920
and polish it.

151
00:07:46,600 --> 00:07:47,920
I like to see things through to the end,

152
00:07:49,120 --> 00:07:50,120
devote myself to one thing,

153
00:07:52,240 --> 00:07:53,199
and love one person.

154
00:07:55,759 --> 00:07:58,199
One wooden figure is too lonely.

155
00:07:58,800 --> 00:08:00,519
On this New Year's Eve,

156
00:08:01,720 --> 00:08:03,240
let's find it a partner,

157
00:08:04,199 --> 00:08:05,199
one that will stay by its side forever.

158
00:08:07,319 --> 00:08:09,439
It's been ages since I got a gift
I liked this much.

159
00:08:09,800 --> 00:08:10,439
How about

160
00:08:10,959 --> 00:08:13,120
we give this pair of carvings a name?

161
00:08:13,639 --> 00:08:15,000
Then we call them

162
00:08:15,319 --> 00:08:16,360
"United Forever in Harmony"

163
00:08:17,079 --> 00:08:17,920
and "Standing Firm, Never Falling".

164
00:08:19,000 --> 00:08:19,920
(It's been a long time
since I've received)

165
00:08:20,040 --> 00:08:21,160
(a gift I loved so much.)

166
00:08:21,480 --> 00:08:22,560
(What would you like in return?)

167
00:08:22,879 --> 00:08:23,759
(Your Highness, how about)

168
00:08:24,480 --> 00:08:26,600
(you give this pair of roly-poly toys
a name?)

169
00:08:27,000 --> 00:08:28,319
(Then we call them)

170
00:08:28,800 --> 00:08:29,959
("United Forever in Harmony")

171
00:08:31,120 --> 00:08:32,080
(and "Standing Firm, Never Falling".)

172
00:08:33,759 --> 00:08:34,480
Why

173
00:08:35,240 --> 00:08:36,519
does this moment feel

174
00:08:37,240 --> 00:08:38,240
like something I've lived through?

175
00:08:38,720 --> 00:08:39,639
It's so familiar.

176
00:08:40,200 --> 00:08:42,080
As if it's already lingered in my memory

177
00:08:42,600 --> 00:08:43,639
for a long time.

178
00:08:44,279 --> 00:08:46,039
This is like a story from a book.

179
00:08:46,679 --> 00:08:48,480
Perhaps in our past lives,

180
00:08:48,799 --> 00:08:51,960
we were already an ordinary couple.

181
00:08:52,240 --> 00:08:54,480
Meeting again in this life,

182
00:08:54,759 --> 00:08:56,759
perhaps it's just us,
reuniting after a long time apart.

183
00:08:57,519 --> 00:08:58,879
Whether it's a story from a book

184
00:08:59,759 --> 00:09:00,960
or the life of an ordinary couple,

185
00:09:01,720 --> 00:09:02,600
I hope we

186
00:09:03,720 --> 00:09:05,480
will have a beautiful
and lasting ending.

187
00:09:12,480 --> 00:09:13,159
So beautiful!

188
00:09:14,039 --> 00:09:14,919
That's stunning!

189
00:09:52,720 --> 00:09:54,480
I want your life!

190
00:09:55,080 --> 00:09:56,440
Should I poison you

191
00:09:57,159 --> 00:09:58,519
or blow you up?

192
00:10:01,200 --> 00:10:02,960
Blowing up would be more satisfying.

193
00:10:04,399 --> 00:10:05,559
(What I have in here)

194
00:10:06,159 --> 00:10:07,480
(has no smell or  taste,)

195
00:10:08,399 --> 00:10:10,679
(the Gut-wrencher.
You'll never see it coming.)

196
00:10:11,120 --> 00:10:12,799
(If you touch one drop of it
by accident,)

197
00:10:12,960 --> 00:10:14,840
(you will bleed all over and die.)

198
00:10:15,000 --> 00:10:16,559
(Slaves like me fear no death,)

199
00:10:17,480 --> 00:10:19,519
(and I'm best at trading life for life.)

200
00:10:19,759 --> 00:10:21,519
(Guards. Drag him out.)

201
00:10:21,720 --> 00:10:23,039
(Your Highness, I am innocent.)

202
00:10:23,240 --> 00:10:24,320
(Show your mercy, Princess!)

203
00:10:24,480 --> 00:10:25,240
(He framed me!)

204
00:10:25,399 --> 00:10:25,679
(Move it!)

205
00:10:25,679 --> 00:10:26,440
(It's him!)

206
00:10:28,759 --> 00:10:30,399
You want my life?

207
00:10:31,000 --> 00:10:32,440
Then we all die!

208
00:10:33,600 --> 00:10:34,519
Your dragonfly kite is so nice!

209
00:10:34,639 --> 00:10:35,320
Mine is better!

210
00:10:35,440 --> 00:10:35,960
But my eagle...

211
00:10:36,080 --> 00:10:36,519
We all die!

212
00:10:36,639 --> 00:10:38,519
- is better than yours.
- Mine is the best!

213
00:10:39,399 --> 00:10:40,480
Despicable wretch!

214
00:10:40,919 --> 00:10:42,039
You're still alive!

215
00:10:42,480 --> 00:10:44,559
You schemed and seduced the Princess

216
00:10:45,120 --> 00:10:46,960
with all your cunning,
and she cherished you so deeply.

217
00:10:47,639 --> 00:10:49,080
Yet you repay her kindness with cruelty,

218
00:10:49,519 --> 00:10:50,840
and you killed the Queen!

219
00:10:51,720 --> 00:10:52,679
I don't know you.

220
00:10:53,200 --> 00:10:54,080
I don't think there's any grievance
between us.

221
00:10:54,320 --> 00:10:55,480
I don't know what you're talking about.

222
00:10:55,679 --> 00:10:56,960
No grievance?

223
00:10:57,840 --> 00:11:00,000
It's your fault

224
00:11:00,000 --> 00:11:01,840
that I've come to this!

225
00:11:02,000 --> 00:11:03,679
This guy is mad. Let's get away.

226
00:11:04,600 --> 00:11:05,200
Your Highness,

227
00:11:05,799 --> 00:11:06,799
today, I will avenge you

228
00:11:07,360 --> 00:11:08,840
and all of Xiling!

229
00:11:16,720 --> 00:11:17,240
Ling Xiao!

230
00:11:27,320 --> 00:11:27,879
I promise

231
00:11:28,240 --> 00:11:29,720
I will get you out of here.

232
00:11:30,559 --> 00:11:31,919
You'll be fine.

233
00:11:33,360 --> 00:11:33,879
Rushi,

234
00:11:34,519 --> 00:11:35,279
I'm sorry.

235
00:11:36,399 --> 00:11:39,919
I couldn't protect you.

236
00:11:40,960 --> 00:11:42,919
Ling Xiao, hold on!

237
00:11:47,519 --> 00:11:48,240
Ling Xiao!

238
00:11:49,440 --> 00:11:50,120
Ling Xiao!

239
00:11:55,080 --> 00:11:59,879
(I want you, for the rest of your life,
to suffer a fate worse than death.)

240
00:12:01,240 --> 00:12:02,559
(I took so much,)

241
00:12:02,879 --> 00:12:04,240
(all for this day)

242
00:12:04,679 --> 00:12:06,519
(to kill you with my own hands.)

243
00:12:06,960 --> 00:12:08,519
(To apologize to your father)

244
00:12:08,919 --> 00:12:10,679
(- and stay with him.
- Mother, no!)

245
00:12:10,759 --> 00:12:12,000
(No!)

246
00:12:13,840 --> 00:12:15,080
(I hate you, Ling Xiao,)

247
00:12:15,519 --> 00:12:16,879
(including this baby.)

248
00:12:16,960 --> 00:12:18,840
(You are the one)

249
00:12:18,840 --> 00:12:20,360
(who made me a monster.)

250
00:12:20,960 --> 00:12:22,440
(We will burn to ash)

251
00:12:22,960 --> 00:12:24,159
(and never,)

252
00:12:24,440 --> 00:12:25,759
(ever meet again!)

253
00:12:30,440 --> 00:12:31,320
Ling Xiao!

254
00:12:33,120 --> 00:12:33,600
Your...

255
00:12:34,120 --> 00:12:35,639
Your hand is injured.

256
00:12:36,320 --> 00:12:37,120
I'm fine.

257
00:12:37,320 --> 00:12:39,000
I will heal you!

258
00:12:39,480 --> 00:12:40,120
Ling Xiao!

259
00:12:41,639 --> 00:12:42,480
Black blood.

260
00:12:43,759 --> 00:12:45,200
The hairpin was poisoned.

261
00:12:45,720 --> 00:12:46,320
If...

262
00:12:47,279 --> 00:12:48,519
If I die,

263
00:12:50,080 --> 00:12:52,120
take good care of yourself.

264
00:12:53,559 --> 00:12:54,480
I suppose

265
00:12:56,679 --> 00:12:57,720
I owe

266
00:12:59,639 --> 00:13:01,200
no debt now.

267
00:13:02,440 --> 00:13:03,159
No!

268
00:13:03,799 --> 00:13:04,679
No!

269
00:13:04,960 --> 00:13:06,240
You promised me!

270
00:13:07,480 --> 00:13:08,399
No!

271
00:13:08,559 --> 00:13:09,360
No!

272
00:13:09,440 --> 00:13:10,200
You promised me

273
00:13:10,200 --> 00:13:12,840
that we would be together forever.

274
00:13:13,240 --> 00:13:14,200
Ling Xiao!

275
00:13:14,840 --> 00:13:16,039
Ling Xiao!

276
00:13:16,720 --> 00:13:18,000
Ling Xiao!

277
00:13:18,200 --> 00:13:20,000
Wake up!

278
00:13:20,080 --> 00:13:21,360
Ling Xiao!
